It goes like yeah, they're being pinched inside their cheek.
就像，嗯，脸颊里面被捏了一下。

90
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:19,240
That's right.
没错。

91
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,240
Those are called dimples.
那些就叫酒窝。

92
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:21,240
Dimples.
酒窝。

93
