有时候人们会自然变秃。

205
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:14,120
Hair falls off as the years go by and no more hair grows on their head.
随着岁月流逝，头发脱落，头上不再长新头发。

206
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:15,120
So they're bald.
所以他们就秃了。

207
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:16,120
That's right.
没错。

208
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:18,300
So this happens to a lot of people, especially men.
这发生在很多人身上，尤其是男人。

209
00:09:18,300 --> 00:09:19,300
They lose their hair.
他们掉头发。

210
00:09:19,300 --> 00:09:20,680
Some people have a little bit of hair.
有些人还有一点头发。

211
00:09:20,680 --> 00:09:22,880
Some people lose all of their hair.
有些人掉光了所有头发。

212
00:09:22,880 --> 00:09:26,680
But when you lose hair on your head, it's called going bald.
但当你头上掉头发时，这叫做变秃。

213
00:09:26,680 --> 00:09:27,680
That's right.
没错。

214
00:09:27,680 --> 00:09:28,680
Okay.
好的。

215
00:09:28,680 --> 00:09:32,280
